pets.name: Luna
pets.description: Luna is a friendly and energetic Havanese who loves to play fetch and cuddle. She's great with kids and other dogs. She's house-trained and knows basic commands.

pets.name: Pepper
pets.description: Pepper is a beautiful cockatiel who loves to whistle and sing. Very friendly and social, enjoys being around people. Comes with cage and toys.

pets.name: Doink
pets.description: Doink is a sweet mixed breed cat with a playful personality. She loves to chase toys and nap in sunny spots. Perfect for apartment living.

pets.name: Buddy
pets.description: Buddy is a loyal Labrador Retriever who loves swimming and outdoor adventures. He's well-trained and great with families.

pets.name: Max
pets.description: Max is a gentle giant who loves everyone he meets. Perfect family dog, great with children, and very obedient.

pets.name: Mittens
pets.description: Mittens is a vocal Siamese who loves attention. She's very affectionate and will follow you around the house.

pets.name: Charlie
pets.description: Charlie is a smart and hypoallergenic Poodle. He's been professionally groomed and knows many tricks.

pets.name: Shadow
pets.description: Shadow is a calm Persian cat who enjoys quiet environments. Perfect for someone looking for a relaxed companion.

pets.name: Tweety
pets.description: Tweety is a beautiful singing canary with a melodious voice. Loves to perform and brighten up your mornings.

pets.name: Rocky
pets.description: Rocky is a protective German Shepherd, great for families looking for security. Well-trained and loyal.

pets.name: Bella
pets.description: Bella is a majestic Maine Coon with a friendly temperament. She's large, fluffy, and loves to play.

pets.name: Daisy
pets.description: Daisy is a sweet mixed breed rescue. She's shy at first but warms up quickly. Looking for a patient, loving home.

pets.name: Bingo
pets.description: Bingo is a vibrant Macaw with stunning colors. He's talkative and loves to entertain. Requires experienced bird owner.

pets.name: Whiskers
pets.description: Whiskers is a calm British Shorthair with a plushy coat. He's independent but loves evening cuddles.

pets.name: Rusty
pets.description: Rusty is an adorable Dutch rabbit who's litter-trained. He loves fresh vegetables and hopping around.

pets.name: Coco
pets.description: Coco is a playful budgie who loves to chirp and play with toys. Great starter bird for families.

pets.name: Spike
pets.description: Spike is a friendly bearded dragon who enjoys being handled. Easy to care for and has a great personality.

pets.name: Ginger
pets.description: Ginger is a beautiful orange tabby with a sweet disposition. She's perfect for someone looking for a lap cat.

pets.name: Cooper
pets.description: Cooper is an energetic mixed breed who loves hiking and adventures. Perfect for an active lifestyle.

pets.name: Thumper
pets.description: Thumper is a fluffy lionhead rabbit with an adorable mane. Very social and loves attention.
